SHANE: What? You gonna start crying now?

53:32.825 --> 53:36.876
Nobody likes a crybaby.

53:36.965 --> 53:38.764
Come on.

53:38.765 --> 53:40.565
- Go on.
- SCOTTY: Come on, James.

53:40.566 --> 53:43.446
You can show me.

53:43.535 --> 53:47.496
Come on, show me the water mill, okay?

53:47.586 --> 53:53.586
(SLAMS TABLE)

53:54.336 --> 54:00.336
Shit!

54:03.607 --> 54:04.956
Yeah.

54:04.957 --> 54:06.576
Cool.

54:06.577 --> 54:09.907
Finally finished it, huh?

54:09.997 --> 54:13.417
Okay.

54:13.507 --> 54:19.507
(WHIRRING)

54:20.527 --> 54:22.868
Hey, how'd you finally get it to work?

54:22.957 --> 54:26.018
Fish tank motor.

54:26.108 --> 54:30.068
Due to air pressure,
it starts up the whole thing and makes it work.

54:30.158 --> 54:32.769
Wow.

54:32.858 --> 54:35.108
I knew you were smart, but...

54:35.198 --> 54:36.277
With brains like that,

54:36.278 --> 54:41.228
I'll bet you actually get to build one of
these for real one day, huh?

54:41.319 --> 54:45.549
Listen.

54:45.639 --> 54:48.789
Look, your father didn't mean what he said,
okay?

54:48.879 --> 54:53.110
He's real proud of you.
He's told me like 100 times.

54:53.199 --> 54:57.789
He called me a crybaby.

54:57.879 --> 54:59.589
Okay.

54:59.590 --> 55:05.590
Look, listen.

55:06.160 --> 55:09.760
All right, I don't know what they told you,
all right?

55:09.850 --> 55:13.540
But the truth is that, um...

55:13.630 --> 55:15.700
I did something stupid, okay?

55:15.790 --> 55:20.291
Something real bad.
That's why I got all beat up.

55:20.381 --> 55:24.071
You know, and right now your father,
he's taking it on the chin.

55:24.161 --> 55:26.591
For me.

55:26.680 --> 55:29.201
So if he gets upset once in a while,
don't blame him.

55:29.291 --> 55:30.640
Blame me, okay?

55:30.641 --> 55:32.711
Well, he's right.

55:32.801 --> 55:37.661
I don't wanna be a crybaby
that gets pushed around.

55:37.752 --> 55:40.632
I wanna be strong like him.

55:40.722 --> 55:43.512
James, you are strong.

55:43.602 --> 55:46.302
Sometimes it takes more guts
walking away from something

55:46.392 --> 55:49.632
than it does duking it out, you know?

55:49.722 --> 55:52.062
You gotta stand up for yourself,

55:52.152 --> 55:55.213
but not with your fists,
with your brains, okay?

55:55.302 --> 55:57.372
Hey, I'll tell you something.

55:57.462 --> 55:59.081
These things?

55:59.082 --> 56:03.043
These things are coming off next week.

56:03.132 --> 56:06.643
You think I could try your scooter?

56:06.733 --> 56:09.523
