56:09.613 --> 56:12.853
You know, until your bones get strong again.

56:12.943 --> 56:16.183
Till I get strong again?
What, you don't think I'm strong now, huh?

56:16.273 --> 56:18.434
Wanna try me out now? Huh, little man?

56:18.523 --> 56:19.693
Come on. Yeah, right.

56:19.694 --> 56:21.223
(SCOTTY LAUGHING)

56:21.224 --> 56:23.384
See, that's what I'm talking about, kid.

56:23.473 --> 56:26.353
Tell you what, race you to school, okay?

56:26.444 --> 56:30.404
Come on! I'll race you to school.

56:30.493 --> 56:31.933
Oh, hey.

56:31.934 --> 56:34.995
Thank you.

56:35.084 --> 56:37.064
Don't worry, he's gonna be fine.

56:37.065 --> 56:42.104
Yeah? And what about Shane?

56:42.194 --> 56:48.194
(CHEERING)

57:31.427 --> 57:37.427
ALL: Oh!

58:07.878 --> 58:13.878
(INAUDIBLE)

58:30.020 --> 58:34.430
Uh, dinner's almost ready.

58:34.520 --> 58:39.110
Where's James?

58:39.201 --> 58:42.531
I asked Scotty to take him
for pizza and a movie.

58:42.620 --> 58:44.780
He was kind of upset.

58:44.870 --> 58:48.651
He lost his baseball cap today.

58:48.741 --> 58:54.741
Shane?

58:55.221 --> 58:57.472
Shane.

58:57.561 --> 58:59.561
I talked to Frank today.

58:59.631 --> 59:01.250
Oh, yeah?

59:01.251 --> 59:04.402
- You call him or he called you?
- No. He called me.

59:04.492 --> 59:07.282
He was pretty upset.

59:07.372 --> 59:11.152
I'm so sorry I hurt his feelings.

59:11.241 --> 59:16.372
Who do you think pays for all of this?

59:16.462 --> 59:20.243
Pizza and movies.

59:20.332 --> 59:22.332
It ain't Danny G no more.

59:22.402 --> 59:24.022
This has got to stop.

59:24.023 --> 59:30.023
You made a deal with him,
and he's not even close to honoring it.

59:36.803 --> 59:41.394
